{
  "text": "In this Section we present the technique of calculating the phononic band structure based on solving the elastic medium wave Equation (1) by the well-known plane wave method (PWM) [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] . In this technique, the differential wave Equation (1), in which the coefficients are periodic functions of two-dimensional position vector ( , ), r x y = is transformed into the reciprocal space.",
  "correct_citation": {
